1. *Navečer* volim da gledam filmove. (In the evening, I like to watch movies.)
2. Ja obično idem u šetnju *navečer*. (I usually take a walk in the evening.)
3. Planiram da učim *navečer*. (I plan to study in the evening.)
4. *Navečer* je veoma hladno u ovom gradu. (It's very cold in this city in the evening.)
5. Molim te da zatvoriš vrata kada izađeš *navečer*. (Please close the door when you leave in the evening.)

Note: In Serbian, "navečer" means "in the evening". It can be used in different forms and positions, depending on the context.